{"type":"text","timestamp":1775881939658,"sessionID":"ses_28531a610ffeGYdPYVZnJRBWyF","part":{"id":"prt_d7acfde41001STNkbIhzjxMtfZ","messageID":"msg_d7acfcb03001yEQlnasU6zF33c","sessionID":"ses_28531a610ffeGYdPYVZnJRBWyF","type":"text","text":"I've created proposal.md for AR-031 RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) in the `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/` directory.\n\nThe proposal includes:\n- **Purpose**: Implement minimum privilege RBAC for secure multi-tenant isolation\n- **Scope**: ServiceAccounts, Roles, RoleBindings for Controller Manager, Workload Manager, Router, and Agentd (with optional ClusterRoles/ClusterRoleBindings)\n- **Impact Analysis**: Security considerations, dependencies, and component impacts\n- **Alternatives Considered**: Shared ServiceAccounts, cluster-wide permissions, wildcards, and dynamic RBAC (all rejected in favor of isolated, namespace-scoped RBAC)\n- **8-phase implementation plan** with detailed tasks and checklists\n- **Testing strategy** covering unit, integration, and E2E tests\n- **Complete API specifications** with YAML examples\n- **Permission matrix** showing component permissions\n- **Security and performance considerations**","time":{"start":1775881939656,"end":1775881939656}}}
